OL,3,CSix police officers to face misconduct
OL,4,Chearings over crash that left three
OL,5,Cdead
OL,7,FSix police officers are set to face
OL,8,Fmisconduct proceedings following an
OL,9,Finvestigation by the Independent
OL,10,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) into
OL,11,Fhow the force handled reports of a
OL,12,Fgroup of missing young people who were
OL,13,Flater found in a crashed car in
OL,14,FCardiff.
OL,16,FThe crash, which happened at around
OL,17,F2am on Saturday 4 March 2023, claimed
OL,18,Fthe lives of Eve Smith, 21, Darcy
OL,19,FRoss, 21, both from Newport, and Rafel
OL,20,FJeanne, 24, from Cardiff.
