OL,3,CSix police officers to face misconduct
OL,4,Chearings over crash that left three
OL,5,Cdead
OL,7,FThe white Volkswagen Tiguan they were
OL,8,Ftravelling in was found almost 48
OL,9,Fhours later, shortly after midnight on
OL,10,FMonday 6 March, in a wooded area off
OL,11,Fthe A48 in St Mellons.
OL,13,FTwo other passengers, Sophie Russon,
OL,14,Fthen 20, and Shane Loughlin, then 32,
OL,15,Fwere seriously injured and taken to
OL,16,Fthe University Hospital of Wales in
OL,17,FCardiff.
OL,19,FAn inquest later heard that all three
OL,20,Fvictims were declared dead at the
OL,21,Fscene.
