OL,4,Chearings over crash that left three
OL,5,Cdead
OL,7,FThe friends had last been seen on a
OL,8,Fnight out in Newport before travelling
OL,9,Fto Porthcawl and later returning
OL,10,Ftowards Cardiff.
OL,12,FWhen they failed to return home,
OL,13,Ffamily members contacted Gwent Police
OL,14,Fto report them missing on 4 and 5
OL,15,FMarch. The car was eventually
OL,16,Fdiscovered after nearly two days of
OL,17,Fsearching.
