OL,3,CSix police officers to face misconduct
OL,4,Chearings over crash that left three
OL,5,Cdead
OL,7,FThe IOPC launched a mandatory
OL,8,Finvestigation to examine how Gwent
OL,9,FPolice handled the missing person
OL,10,Freports, including whether officers
OL,11,Fcarried out appropriate risk
OL,12,Fassessments, reviews and searches.
OL,14,FThe IOPC also reviewed more than 30
OL,15,Fcomplaints made by the families of
OL,16,Fthose involved about how both Gwent
OL,17,FPolice and South Wales Police handled
OL,18,Fthe investigation.
