OL,7,FIOPC Director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,8,F"Our thoughts and sympathies remain
OL,9,Fwith the young people who tragically
OL,10,Flost their lives, those who were left
OL,11,Fseriously injured and everyone
OL,12,Faffected by this incident. This
OL,13,Finvestigation has been complex and
OL,14,Fresource-intensive, but it is
OL,15,Fimportant for public confidence in
OL,16,Fpolicing that this tragic incident was
OL,17,Fsubject to thorough and independent
OL,18,Fscrutiny."
