OL,7,FIn a statement, Deputy Chief Constable
OL,8,Fof Gwent Police Nicky Brain said: "Our
OL,9,Fthoughts and condolences continue to
OL,10,Fbe with the family and friends of
OL,11,FDarcy, Eve and Rafel who tragically
OL,12,Flost their lives and those who
OL,13,Fsustained injuries that night.
OL,15,F"We acknowledge the impact that this
OL,16,Finvestigation has had on them and
OL,17,Funderstand how important the findings
OL,18,Fof the Independent Office for Police
OL,19,FConduct (IOPC) will be to all those
OL,20,Faffected and the wider community.
