OL,7,F"We have fully co-operated with the
OL,8,FIOPC in their investigation. It's
OL,9,Fimportant that these matters were
OL,10,Finvestigated thoroughly in an open and
OL,11,Ftransparent manner.
OL,13,F"We will now start the process to hold
OL,14,Fthe relevant misconduct hearings and
OL,15,Fmisconduct meetings."
